+        // trade fee tx: 260 bytes (1 input)
+        // deposit tx: 336 bytes (1 MS output+ OP_RETURN) - 414 bytes (1 MS output + OP_RETURN + change in case of smaller trade amount)
+        // payout tx: 371 bytes
+        // disputed payout tx: 408 bytes
